{"data":[{"name":"79:1","price":"1. Bij degenen (de engelen) die met grote kracht (de slechte ziel) eruit trekken.","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰزِعَٰتِ غَرۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5713,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:2","price":"2. Bij degenen die dat zachtjes doen (bij de goede zielen).","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِطَٰتِ نَشۡطٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5714,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:3","price":"3. En bij degenen die zweven.","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِحَٰتِ سَبۡحٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5715,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:4","price":"4. En bij degenen die altijd als eerste aankomen.","arabic":"فَٱلسَّٰبِقَٰتِ سَبۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5716,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:5","price":"5. En bij hen die de bevelen van hun Heer opvolgen.","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُدَبِّرَٰتِ أَمۡرٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5717,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:6","price":"6. Op de dag zullen de aarde en de bergen heftig bewegen.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَرۡجُفُ ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5718,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:7","price":"7. Wat gevolgd wordt door een tweede.","arabic":"تَتۡبَعُهَا ٱلرَّادِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5719,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:8","price":"8. Op die dag zullen harten trillen van angst.","arabic":"قُلُوبٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاجِفَةٌ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5720,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:9","price":"9. Hun ogen zullen neergeslagen zijn.","arabic":"أَبۡصَٰرُهَا خَٰشِعَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5721,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:10","price":"10. Zij zeggen: “Zullen wij waarlijk terugkeren naar onze eerste staat?”","arabic":"يَقُولُونَ أَءِنَّا لَمَرۡدُودُونَ فِي ٱلۡحَافِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5722,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:11","price":"11. \"Zelfs nadat wij verpulverde botten zijn geweest?”","arabic":"أَءِذَا كُنَّا عِظَٰمٗا نَّخِرَةٗ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5723,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:12","price":"12. Zij zeggen: “In dat geval is de terugkeer een verlies!”","arabic":"قَالُواْ تِلۡكَ إِذٗا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5724,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:13","price":"13. Maar het is slechts een enkele roep.","arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5725,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:14","price":"14. Ziedaar! Zij zullen zichzelf levend op aarde treffen na hun dood.","arabic":"فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5726,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:15","price":"15. Is het verhaal van Moesa tot jou gekomen?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5727,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:16","price":"16. Toen zijn Heer hem in de heilige Toewadal tot zich riep?","arabic":"إِذۡ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلۡوَادِ ٱلۡمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5728,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:17","price":"17. Ga naar de Farao, waarlijk hij heeft alle grenzen overschreden (in misdaad, zonden, polytheïsme, ongeloof).","arabic":"ٱذۡهَبۡ إِلَىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5729,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:18","price":"18. En zeg tegen hem: “Zou je jezelf willen reinigen (van de zonde van ongeloof door een gelovige te worden),”","arabic":"فَقُلۡ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5730,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:19","price":"19. En dat ik je naar je Heer zal leiden, zodat je Hem zal vrezen?”","arabic":"وَأَهۡدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخۡشَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5731,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:20","price":"20. Toen toonde (Moesa) hem de grote tekenen (de wonderen).","arabic":"فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلۡأٓيَةَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5732,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:21","price":"21. Maar hij verloochende (hen) en was ongehoorzaam.","arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5733,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:22","price":"22. Toen keerde hij zijn rug toe en hard (tegen Allah) vechtend.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5734,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:23","price":"23. Toen verzamelde hij mensen en riep luid:","arabic":"فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5735,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:24","price":"24. Zeggende: “Ik ben jullie heer, de hoogste.”","arabic":"فَقَالَ أَنَا۠ رَبُّكُمُ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5736,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:25","price":"25. Daarom greep Allah hem met een bestraffing voor deze laatste overtreding.","arabic":"فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ نَكَالَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5737,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:26","price":"26. Waarlijk, hierin is een instructieve vermaning voor ieder die Allah vreest.","arabic":"إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبۡرَةٗ لِّمَن يَخۡشَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5738,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:27","price":"27. Zijn jullie moeilijker te scheppen, of is dat de hemel die Hij gebouwd heeft?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُۚ بَنَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5739,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:28","price":"28. Hij heeft haar (de hemel) hoog opgetrokken en perfekt gemaakt.","arabic":"رَفَعَ سَمۡكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5740,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:29","price":"29. De nacht daarvan bedekt Hij met duisternis en in haar ochtend brengt Hij (het licht).","arabic":"وَأَغۡطَشَ لَيۡلَهَا وَأَخۡرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5741,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:30","price":"30. Daarna heeft Hij de aarde uitgespreid.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5742,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:31","price":"31. En heeft daaruit haar water en weiden voortgebracht.","arabic":"أَخۡرَجَ مِنۡهَا مَآءَهَا وَمَرۡعَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5743,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:32","price":"32. En de bergen heeft Hij stevig vastgezet.","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5744,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:33","price":"33. Om een genieting en een nut voor jullie en jullie vee te zijn.","arabic":"مَتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5745,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:34","price":"34. Maar als de grootste ramp aanbreekt (het begin van de dag des oordeels).","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلطَّآمَّةُ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5746,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:35","price":"35. De dag waarop de mens zich zal herinneren waarnaar hij heeft gestreefd.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5747,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:36","price":"36. En het hellevuur zal voor iedereen die ziet duidelijk worden.","arabic":"وَبُرِّزَتِ ٱلۡجَحِيمُ لِمَن يَرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5748,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:37","price":"37. Dan, voor degenen die de grenzen overtreden.","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5749,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:38","price":"38. En de voorkeur aan het wereldse leven gaven.","arabic":"وَءَاثَرَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5750,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:39","price":"39. Waarlijk, hun verblijfplaats zal het hellevuur zijn.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5751,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:40","price":"40. Maar voor degenen die angst hadden om voor hun Heer te staan, en zichzelf verre hielden van onreine, kwade wensen en lusten.","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ وَنَهَى ٱلنَّفۡسَ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5752,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:41","price":"41. Waarlijk, hun verblijfplaats is het paradijs.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَنَّةَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5753,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:42","price":"42. Zij vragen jou over het uur – wanneer is de aangewezen tijd?","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلسَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5754,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:43","price":"43. Jij (o Mohammed) hebt geen kennis om hierover iets te zeggen.","arabic":"فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكۡرَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5755,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:44","price":"44. Aan jouw Heer behoort (de kennis van) de termijn hiervan.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ مُنتَهَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5756,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:45","price":"45. Jij bent slechts een waarschuwer voor degenen die ervoor vrezen.","arabic":"إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُنذِرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5757,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"79:46","price":"46. De dag dat zij het aanschouwen, (zal het lijken) alsof zij niet langer (in het wereldse leven) verbleven dan een avond of een ochtend.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ يَوۡمَ يَرَوۡنَهَا لَمۡ يَلۡبَثُوٓاْ إِلَّا عَشِيَّةً أَوۡ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5758,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"}],"chapter":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at","Chapter An-Nazi'at","Nazi'at","Surah Nazi'at","Chapter Nazi'at","An Nazi'at","Surah An Nazi'at","Chapter An Nazi'at","Surah 79","Chapter 79","Those Who Pull Out","النازعات"]}